is also a metric.

=== Conditional mutual information ===

Sometimes it is useful to express the mutual information of two random variables conditioned on a third.

( P_{(X,Y)|Z} \| P_{X|Z} \otimes P_{Y|Z} )]&lt;/math&gt;
